com.aevi.payment

Class PaymentAppConfigurationRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aevi.helpers.BundleWrapper
      • com.aevi.payment.PaymentAppConfigurationRequest

  • public class PaymentAppConfigurationRequest
extends BundleWrapper
    The PaymentAppConfigurationRequest object represents a request made to the payment application for configuration data. 

     
 startActivityForResult(PaymentAppConfigurationRequest.createIntent(), 0);

    PaymentAppConfiguration requests are used to return the PaymentAppConfiguration data for the Payment App.

    Note:This Intent based mechanism is necessary due to the security sandboxing of the Payment Application

    See Also:
    PaymentAppConfiguration
